{"tid":2057012,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"雙螢幕問題","createTime":"2020-06-09T05:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T13:59:30.000Z","uid":156133,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"764b142cbd33fc8531893e1b6f1ce161d02af966","tid":2057012,"uid":156133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"最近出咗部新機用NVIDIA顯卡, 開機果陣BIOS畫面會出去用DP果個Mon到<br />\n原先用DP嘅係我副Mon嚟, 為咗出返去主Mon, 我兩條線對換咗啦<br />\n於是依家BIOS畫面出喺我主Mon到...<br />\n但係喺Windows入面, 佢話我主Mon係&quot;2&quot;, 副Mon係&quot;1&quot;<br />\n咁都算, 我將&quot;2&quot;剔咗&quot;使其成為主顯示器&quot;<br />\n但係用Win+P揀&quot;僅電腦螢幕&quot;, 佢會出咗喺我副Mon...<br />\n我每次想只用主Mon都要揀&quot;僅第二個螢幕&quot;, 好唔方便...<br />\n而且強迫症, 想將主Mon變返&quot;1&quot;, 有冇辦法將佢識別嘅&quot;1&quot;/&quot;2&quot;序號調返轉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/09/TSb8ut.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2FTSb8ut.png&h=a3e69356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/09/HrWwQ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2FHrWwQ9.png&h=55c6a400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/09/743R9r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2F743R9r.png&h=cd29cf88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nP.S. 之前砌完部機試機果陣係直接經HDMI駁電視機裝Windows同Driver<br />\n後來先搬返入房駁兩個Mon, 依家HDMI係&quot;1&quot;, DP係&quot;2&quot;, 有冇關係？<br />\n佢個次序係唔係因為咁而跟咗？<br />\n如果我抆咗HDMI, 經DP個Mon重裝Windows同Driver之後先再駁返個HDMI, 咁個順序係咪會正常返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新機唔想隨便洗機試, 好似好傷SSD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a47f29bc690840bd5cf835d1c37859cc0d8c545","tid":2057012,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"負皮上一頁"},{"pid":"0351831732114b627db215b729348ec86e7a557c